What you need to know:

Aguero himself is adamant his departure does not mean the end of the story for him personally.Barcelona are reported to be potential suitors and the Argentine has also been linked with Paris Saint-Germain, Juventus and Inter Milan.City, for their part, hope to have thousands of fans back in their stadium as Covid-19 restrictions are eased -- in time to say farewell to Aguero and give a fitting send-off to one of their true greats.